{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/Details_page_GIF02.gif?t=1737028546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Wanme Times \u2013 the ever-evolving game workshop! We create games with creativity, constantly updating the levels of The \u201cPOCKET ORACLE\u201d, enhancing the fun, building a rich game ecosystem, and providing a lasting gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 POCKET ORACLE \u2013 Useful every day, foreseeing a different kind of excitement!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/banner_grimm-19.png?t=1737028546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Explore the Wisdom of the 64 Hexagrams</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Inspired by Taoist philosophy and the I Ching, *POCKET ORACLE* is an interactive divination game that offers easy-to-understand insights. Unlock the meanings of 64 hexagrams and gain valuable guidance on love, career, health, and wealth\u2014shaping your journey with every choice you make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/banner_grimm-E-01.png?t=1737028546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Talk to your personal guide NPC, &quot;Fuxi,&quot; who will interpret the hexagrams and provide insightful, practical advice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Unlock prophecies through tasks. Your choices shape your destiny, and the power to change your future is in your hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"h